  "abstract": "This is the first annual report of the International Crops Research\r\nInstitute for the Semi-Arid Tropics which has been printed for\r\nworldwide distribution. The report gives research highlights for the\r\nperiod from 1 April 1973 to 31 March 1974. A report for our first\r\nyear of operation (1972—73) covered preliminary investigations'of\r\nFarming Systems, the single program which began activities that year.",
